Sidney Morgan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sidney_Morgan 0 Sydney Morgan (31 October 1883 – 5 December 1931) was an Irish stage and screen actor. He was an actor for many years with the Abbey Theatre in Dublin. Among his most celebrated performances was as Joxer in Sean O'Casey's original production of Juno and the Paycock. He repeated his role to acclaim on the screen in the Alfred Hitchcock film Juno and the Paycock. He was born in Dublin, Ireland and died in Surrey Sydney_Morgan ( 31_October_1883 – 5_December_1931 ) was an_Irish_stage_and_screen_actor .
